description:
Doesn't hurt to work
together sometimes,
I guess. I'll lend you
a hand, too.

Here you can work together with
others and engage in battle.
I am certain you will play
a very active role, my lord.

This is a Co-op Battle
where you play together
with lots of people!
Good luck! ☆
Think carefully\nwhen spending Jewels.\nDon't waste them!

My lord, you can purchase
valuable items using Jewels.
However, you must be
careful not to overspend.
Jewels can be exchanged\nfor delicious fo—\nI mean, valuable items!

You can receive rewards
when you achieve
certain goals!
Good luck! ♪

Looks like it's full of
memories. We've been
through a lot, but it doesn't
hurt to look back sometimes.

Here we can look back
again and again...
on our happy days
together! ♪

You can relive your memories
with all the girls in your life!
Whoop, whoop! ♪
Way to go, Mr. Popular! ☆

You can also receive
items by clearing
quests.
Let's take all we can!

In this quest, you can earn
items required for Training.
I will become stronger
for you, my lord.

You'll receive some nice items
for clearing this quest!
Collect as many as you
can and get super strong!

My lord, let us prepare
for our journey.
It will make for an even
more fulfilling adventure.

Looks like you can join
a Clan.
Why not give it a try?
Could be a lot of fun! ♪

You can join a Clan here.
There are so many
wonderful Clans,
it is difficult to choose.

Want to join a Clan?
It's a lot more fun
going on adventures
as a team!

Here you can look back
at the activities of
friends who participated
in Clan Battles.

Looks like you can
save Battle Records
of your favorite
practice runs.

My lord, your activities
in this Clan Battle have
been recorded. You can now
review them for future battles.

You can go over your
Battle Record for this
Clan Battle!
Let me have a look too!

Hello there!
In this section, you can choose
new music to play on your home
screen or in the guildhouse!

If you're looking to change the
BGM or buy new tracks, you've
come to the right place! We have
a wide selection available!

You can choose all sorts of tracks
to play on your home screen or in
the guildhouse! Why don't you
show me some of your favorites?

This is where you can change
your background music settings!
What kind of track are you after?
Haha, I can't wait to hear it!

This is where you can purchase
new music tracks to use!
You can listen to a sample first,
so feel free to take your time.

Always a pleasure to see you!
Welcome to the music store.
There are so many lovely tracks,
it can be hard to choose, can't it?
